What happens when you cross an undead assassin with a katana-wielding monkey who has a grudge to settle? You get the blood-soaked saga of Marvel’s Hit Monkey, the very adult animated Hulu original that snuck under the radar of most comic fans. It's a different kind of show than Marvel's Disney plus efforts but is it any good? Well, we ain't monkeying around in this review! Join us as we discuss in great detail the entire first season of Hit Monkey, and debate whether it deserves a second season!  Please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [ComicBookClique.com](episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

